</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="vi8dv7" data-video-descrip="Treasure somehow makes their game's Bacterion leader even more pathetic than Gofer was." data-video-title="Gradius V (Venom)" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/vi8dv7_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/vi8dv7.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/AnticlimaxBoss" data-video-tropename="Anti-Climax Boss" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/Gradius" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/vi8dv7.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Gradius V (Venom)</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="1d2tvs" data-video-descrip="...Again, Gofer? For the self-proclaimed &amp;quot;center of the universe&amp;quot;, you're content to just let a ship destroy you." data-video-title="Gradius IV (Gofer)" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/1d2tvs_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/1d2tvs.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/AnticlimaxBoss" data-video-tropename="Anti-Climax Boss" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/Gradius" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/1d2tvs.jpg">
